OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine end
OL,6,Fto the day, with plenty of warm
OL,7,Fsunshine and light winds. Staying dry
OL,8,Fwith prolonged clear skies overnight.
OL,9,FLight and variable winds. Staying mild.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTuesday:FGenerally dry with variable
OL,12,Fcloud, temperatures will be lower than
OL,13,Fof late, especially along the coast as
OL,14,Fa breezy onshore wind develops.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,17,FGenerally dry with variable cloud on
OL,18,FWednesday and Thursday. Some sunny
OL,19,Fintervals on Friday and breezy along
OL,20,Fthe coast. Temperatures remain warm
OL,21,Fbut feeling cooler along the coasts.
